   version stable 20110601
  category administration/spell
 attribute archive_off console
      info home  http://sorcerer.silverice.org/
      desc "disk full protection

immune-sentinel-space is part of the Sorcerer immune system.
It runs on the Sorcerer's keep.
It periodically checks available space
in areas of the root file system.
It might remove or compress directories,
but will probably not cause problems."

build(){
 mkdir  -pvm 755                            $DESTDIR/usr/sbin
 install -vm 700 $SCRIPT_DIR/sentinel-space $DESTDIR/usr/sbin
}
